## [Visual Studio / .NET]
bin/
obj/
appsettings.Development.json
out/
publish/

## [Node / Vue / Quasar]
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/
dist/
dist-ssr/
.quasar/
*.local
.eslintcache
.stylelintcache
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
